{"id":195267,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/11/维权网-网络调查：83的人在投票前没见过候选人/","date":"2011-11-10T16:00:48Z","modified":"2011-11-10T16:00:48Z","title":"维权网 | 网络调查：83%的人在投票前没见过候选人","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span>    </span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a>（维权网信息员德明报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，网民在新浪微博上发起了一次网络调查，调查名为“我经历过的选举”，调查问题包括<span>“投票前见过候选人”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“投票前没见过候选人”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“投票前知道候选人的竞选主张与承诺”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“投票前不知道候选人的竞选主张与承诺”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“投票前有人告诉我投给谁”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“投票前没人告诉我投给谁”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“投票时我按顺序勾选候选人”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“投票时我按倒序勾选候选人”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“我投过反对票”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“我未投反对票”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“我投给过候选人以外的公民”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>、“</span></span><span>领到过选民证，但放弃了投票”等十二项。</span><span>到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>时</span><span>，已有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">507</span><span>人参与，其中有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">421</span><span>人表示“<span>投票前没见过候选人”，占总数的</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">83%</span></span><span><span>；“投票前不知道候选人的竞选主张与承诺”的有</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">428</span></span><span><span>人，占总数的</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">84%</span></span><span><span>；有</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">224 </span></span><span><span>人表示“</span></span><span><span>投票前有人告诉我投给谁”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>，占总数的</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">44%</span></span><span><span>；只有</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">42</span></span><span><span>人表示“</span></span><span><span>我投给过候选人以外的公民”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>，占</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8% </span></span><span><span>；表示“</span></span><span><span>领到过选民证，但放弃了投票”的有</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">111</span></span><span><span>人，占</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22% </span></span><span><span>。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>调查表明，大部分人在投票前对候选人一无所知，甚至连面也没见过。而有将近一半人的选票是在“</span></span><span><span>投票前有人告诉我投给谁”的情况下投出的，对这句话的含义，中国人都懂得的。只有</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8%</span></span><span><span>的人“</span></span><span><span>投给过候选人以外的公民”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>，表明在以往的选举中，官定的正式候选人基本上垄断了选票，也表明选民的意志基本上被官方操控。而</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22%</span></span><span><span>的人“</span></span><span><span>领到过选民证，但放弃了投票”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>，反映出人们对所谓“选举”的冷漠。一位网民说，“</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1980</span><span>年，第一次拿到选民证，让自行去看候选人简历后再去投票，顿生厌恶。不知他是谁，主张是什么，如何代表我？此后至今，我自愿或不自愿地放弃了所有的投票（其中有几年和今年没有见到选民证），并以此为骄傲。在直接选举没来临之前，将一直放弃，直到死亡。”网民“章劲”说，“本世纪以来，所有的人大代表选举均选择了弃权，因为我不认识这些候选人，也不知道他们是否能代表我的利益。”</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在另一项“年满</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>岁未领到选票的公民请举手”的调查中，目前已有近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1400</span><span>人参与。调查的问题是，“基层人大选举每五年一届，不少网友却反映自己从未行使过选举权。如果你今年已满</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>岁，未被依法剥夺政治权利，从未领到选票也未被告知享有选举权，请举手。”在这些“从未领到选票也未被告知享有选举权”的人中，有</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">41%</span></span><span><span>是</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span></span><span><span>后，而</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span></span><span><span>后乃至</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span></span><span><span>后、</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span></span><span><span>后的“</span></span><span>压根就没见过选票是啥样子的<span>”</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span>也大有人在。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://weibo.com/1095441657\" title=\"燕瀛居士\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">网民</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">“燕瀛居士”说，</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span></span></a></span><span>一没见过选票，二没见过候选人。而且我基本可以确定我父母（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>后）跟我一样，一生‘被选举’。”</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>网民章立凡说，“</span></span><span>回顾一下你有生以来的投票经历，会发现很多问题。是中国人自己不会行使民主？还是我们的制度设计有问题？”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7229218769831518691?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[14397]}